---
title: Kentucky-Style Fried Chicken & Fries with Creamy Bacon-Apple Slaw & Onion Jus
description: Time to unleash your inner chef! We’re all familiar with the smell of Kentucky fried chicken, but have you ever made it from
scratch? Chicken drumsticks are lightly coated in flour and spices before being shallow fried to golden, crispy perfection. Paired
with classics like fries, slaw and onion jus, this meal is a taste of nostalgia.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66a476abba0a03f5866542e2-af4ee367.jpeg
